#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:31
msgid ""
"Be sure to check out the [Unchained](https://rebellion.global/"
"blog/2020/06/18/xr-unchained-15) for an array of more brave and beautiful "
"actions from across the globe."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:33
msgid ""
"Our announcements section is bursting with ways to educate yourself and get "
"involved, whether that’s helping out with the [new website redesign](https://"
